<c74object name='dk.buf2list' category='' module='dataknot'>
    <digest>Copy the contents of a buffer~ to a list
</digest>
    <description>A simplified workflow for extracting numerical data from buffers as lists of numbers.
</description>
    <discussion>Given a source <o>buffer~</o> that is valid, <o>dk.buf2list</o> copies its contents to a new list when it receives the input.<br/> This is a convenient way of extracting data from a <o>list</o>
</discussion>

